      <h2>Three Tradie Profiles That Need Call Recovery Most</h2>
      <p>Not every trade business needs call recovery right away. But if any of these three profiles describe your situation, you are bleeding leads every single day:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>The solo operator:</strong> You answer your own phone while on job sites. Every call you miss during a job is a lead you paid for that goes to voicemail. A recovery system acts as your after-hours and on-site receptionist</li>
        <li><strong>The multi-truck owner:</strong> You have 3–10 trucks on the road and a dispatcher who cannot keep up. Overflow calls during peak season hit voicemail. A recovery system catches every overflow call and books it</li>
        <li><strong>The off-hours advertiser:</strong> You run Google Ads 24/7 on a $100+/day budget but only answer calls during business hours. You are paying for leads that arrive at night and disappear by morning</li>
      </ul>

