      <p>Tradies who deploy a call recovery system consistently report the same outcomes within the first 30 days. Appointment volume increases 40–60% from previously missed calls. Morning inbox chaos disappears because appointments were already booked overnight. And Google Ads cost-per-lead trends downward as the algorithm registers more conversions from the same spend.</p>
      <p>The fix is not complicated. It does not require hiring staff or changing how you run ads. It requires one change: making sure every call that comes in gets answered, qualified, and booked — automatically, every time.</p>

